# Express.js RESTful API – Product Management

## API Endpoints

- `GET /api/products` – Get all products
- `GET /api/products/:id` – Get single product
- `POST /api/products` – Create product (requires `Bearer secret`)
- `PUT /api/products/:id` – Update product (requires `Bearer secret`)
- `DELETE /api/products/:id` – Delete product (requires `Bearer secret`)

